<p><strong>The Scorecard</strong></p>
<p><span><span>~ 28 members signed up for <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/events/297852222/">Career Essentials in Generative AI</a></strong><br />~ 5 members have made the commitment to begin by posting to <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/54055597/">Introduce Yourself</a></strong><br />~ 3 members have completed Sprint #1 &gt; <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/54055638/">What Is Generative AI?<br /></a></strong></span></span>~ 3 members have completed Sprint #2 &gt; <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/54060091/">Generative AI: The Evolution of Thoughtful Online Search<br /></a></strong>~ 3 members have completed Sprint #3 &gt; <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/54067134/">Streamlining Your Work with Copilot</a></strong></p>
<p>This is the fourth of six weekly sprints. Once you complete the fourth course (Sprint #4), post a message, along with a link to your certificate of completion in the <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/54074696/">Learning Microsoft 365 Copilot</a> </strong>discussion area.</p>
<p>If you feel like you are now three touchdowns behind, there is no need to despair. You may begin whenever you feel you are ready to begin. Simply gain access to <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/learning/paths/career-essentials-in-generative-ai-by-microsoft-and-linkedin"><strong>Career Essentials in Generative AI by Microsoft and LinkedIn</strong></a>. This learning path has been made available for <strong>FREE</strong> for a limited time. Once you complete each sprint you will receive a certificate to post to your LinkedIn profile. A complete list of all weekly sprints can be found in <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/54054010">Master Discussion List—Career Essentials in Generative AI</a></strong>. Post any questions you might have in the <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/54055597/">Introduce Yourself</a></strong> discussion area.</p>
<p>Let's get artificially intelligent!</p>
